  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/58411664af296098635729d8525e6bc7.avif?t=1773872514\" width=630 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a realm where power is hoarded behind ancient laws, the Gatekeepers decide who is worthy of magic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They chose wrong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter <strong>Slayqueen: The Gatekeeper</strong>, an epic fantasy card game where forbidden spells, summoned beasts, and living legends are locked behind cruel tradition. Collect arcane cards ripped from sealed vaults, challenge the Gatekeepers who police magic itself, and rise through a world that would rather see you kneel than ascend.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/95700aa13780924ef08d097f36dcb714.poster.avif?t=1773872514\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/95700aa13780924ef08d097f36dcb714.webm?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/95700aa13780924ef08d097f36dcb714.mp4?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/8eb3da2d47674b7ffe62d490d0d1330d.poster.avif?t=1773872514\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/8eb3da2d47674b7ffe62d490d0d1330d.webm?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/8eb3da2d47674b7ffe62d490d0d1330d.mp4?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each duel is a trial. Each card a stolen secret. <br>Defeat the Gatekeepers. <br>Slay the Queen. <br>Claim a magic they swore you would never wield.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/f4d920f38a6a1838f5653043fb5b89d8.poster.avif?t=1773872514\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/f4d920f38a6a1838f5653043fb5b89d8.webm?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/f4d920f38a6a1838f5653043fb5b89d8.mp4?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/58411664af296098635729d8525e6bc7.avif?t=1773872514\" width=630 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a realm where power is hoarded behind ancient laws, the Gatekeepers decide who is worthy of magic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They chose wrong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter <strong>Slayqueen: The Gatekeeper</strong>, an epic fantasy card game where forbidden spells, summoned beasts, and living legends are locked behind cruel tradition. Collect arcane cards ripped from sealed vaults, challenge the Gatekeepers who police magic itself, and rise through a world that would rather see you kneel than ascend.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/95700aa13780924ef08d097f36dcb714.poster.avif?t=1773872514\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/95700aa13780924ef08d097f36dcb714.webm?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/95700aa13780924ef08d097f36dcb714.mp4?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/8eb3da2d47674b7ffe62d490d0d1330d.poster.avif?t=1773872514\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/8eb3da2d47674b7ffe62d490d0d1330d.webm?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/8eb3da2d47674b7ffe62d490d0d1330d.mp4?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each duel is a trial. Each card a stolen secret. <br>Defeat the Gatekeepers. <br>Slay the Queen. <br>Claim a magic they swore you would never wield.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/f4d920f38a6a1838f5653043fb5b89d8.poster.avif?t=1773872514\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/f4d920f38a6a1838f5653043fb5b89d8.webm?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4345100/extras/f4d920f38a6a1838f5653043fb5b89d8.mp4?t=1773872514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
